%o A332542 end
%o A332542 p A332542(100) # _Seiichi Manyama_, Feb 19 2020
%o A332542 (PARI) a(n) = my(k=1); while (sum(i=0, k, n+i) % (n+k+1), k++); k; \\ _Michel Marcus_, Aug 26 2021
